description: Demolition of the existing student hostel building (Sui Generis) and replacement with a part 4, 6, 7, 10 storey building plus basement to provide extra-care accommodation for older people (Class C3), comprising 60 flats and associated communal facilities including restaurant, lounges, health and well-being facility and staff facilities, plus basement level carparking, cycle and mobility scooter parking, basement and 10th floor plant, ground floor communal gardens, and 3rd & 6th floor roof terraces.
